  m_Name: The AI Artist
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Character
  characterName: AI Artist
  characterDescription: "You think Enjin shouldn\u2019t be discussed, it should be
    used. Moreover, you think that if Enjin isn\u2019t used, the sector will fall
    behind. You care more about what you create, than that you created it.\n\nThink
    about how you're going to push for Enjin implementation within the company. 
    How can Enjin boost productivity? How can it make people's lives more efficient?
    Get in character! \r\n"
